              <h3 lang="y">천의 넓이는 몇 ㎡인가요?</h3>
              <div class="input_wrap answer7 hint_120">
                <math-field data-answer-single="0.48"></math-field>
                <p class="f32b">㎡</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <div class="btn_area">
